data.name: label14.Text
data.value: Description: An apartment management system aims to streamline the management of apartment complexes by facilitating efficient communication between tenants, property managers, and maintenance staff. It enables effective tenant management, maintenance tracking, financial management, security and access control, facility management, legal compliance, and data analytics. By automating tasks and centralizing information, the system enhances operational efficiency, improves tenant satisfaction, and ensures the smooth functioning of the property.
